  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, whisk together yogurt, olive oil, garlic, salt, and pepper.",
    "3. Add lamb cubes to the marinade and mix well to coat.",
    "4. Cover bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "5. Thread lamb cubes, spring onions, and parsley onto skewers.",
    "6. Brush skewers with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "7. Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until lamb reaches 145°F (63°C).",
    "8. Serve immediately, garnished with additional parsley if desired.",
    "9. If desired, serve with a drizzle of robust red wine."
